projectDesc.p: JOS - jezikoslovno označevanje slovenskega jezika, http://nl.ijs.si/jos/
JOS - linguistic annotation of the Slovene language, http://nl.ijs.si/jos/

samplingDecl.p: Sampling for this corpus was performed in two steps. First, complete documents were sampled from FidaPLUS (600M words), to make a corpus of 100M words; at this stage, FidaPLUS MSDs were converted to JOS MSDs. Second, isolated paragraphs were sampled from the 100M corpus, to arrive at 1M words.

Korpus je bil vzorčen v dveh korakih. Najprej so bili vzorčeni celotna besedila s korpusa FidaPLUS (600M besed), s čimer smo dobili korpus velik 100M besed; v tem koraku so bile oblikoslovne oznake FidaPLUS pretvorjene v oznake JOS. V drugem koraku so bili vzorčeni posamezni odstavki iz korpusa 100M, dokler ni bilo zbranih 1.000.000 besed.

correction.p: No correction was performed on the text.

quotation.p: Quotation marks have been left in the text, and are not explicitly marked up.
Navednice so del besedila, besedilo znotraj navednic ni posebej označeno.

segmentation.p: The texts are segmented into paragraphs, sentences, words and punctuation as in the source FidaPLUS corpus, by software produced by Amebis.
Besedila so razdeljena v odstavke, stavke, besede in ločila kot v izvornem korpusu FidaPLUS, s programjem Amebis, d.o.o.

interpretation.p: Words are annotated by context-disambiguated morphosyntactic description and lemma. The annotation was first performed by Amebis in FidaPLUS. The texts were subsequently re-tagged, and where the new annotations differed from those of Amebis, they were manually checked. The automatically assigned annotations are marked by w/@type='auto', the manually validated ones by w/@type='manual'.

Besede so označene s kontekstno razdvoumljenimi oblikoslovnimi oznakami in lemami. Označevanje je bilo narejeno avtomatsko v okviru korpusa FidaPLUS s strani Amebis, d.o.o. Besedila so bila naknadno ponovno avtomatsko označena, in kjer so se nove oznake razlikovale od Amebisovih, so bile ročno pregledane. Avtomatsko pripisanim oznakam je dodan w/@type='auto', ročnim pa w/@type='manual'.

stdVals.p: The two-letter language codes follow ISO 639 and are defined in the language usage element.
Dvočrkovne kode jezikov sledijo ISO 639 in so definirane v elementu uporabe jezikov.
Morphosyntactic descriptions follow the JOS morphosyntactic specification V1.1, c.f. http://nl.ijs.si/jos/msd/
Oblikoslovne oznake sledijo priporočilom za oblikoskladenjsko označevanje JOS V1.1, c.f. http://nl.ijs.si/jos/msd/
